com.att.android.arodatacollector.main
Class AROCollectorTaskManagerProcessInfo

java.lang.Object
  com.att.android.arodatacollector.main.AROCollectorTaskManagerProcessInfo

public class AROCollectorTaskManagerProcessInfo
extends java.lang.Object

Represents task killer process information for the ARO Data Collector. This class maintains a collection of AROCollectorTaskManagerProcessInfo.PsRow classes that contain native shell command (PS) output.

Returns a value indicating whether or not tcpdump is running on the native shell.

Returns:

getPsRow

public AROCollectorTaskManagerProcessInfo.PsRow getPsRow(java.lang.String cmd)
Returns the specified row of task killer process information. Each row represents the output from a native shell command.

Parameters:
cmd - A string containing the native shell command to return the output for.
Returns:
An AROCollectorTaskManagerProcessInfo.PsRow object containing the output for the specified native shell command.
